strings: <voice_0x01001BAA><se_low>It's Maurice.: Do you like that right? I place this idol on this great beast. Then the world will see your crazy tastes and desires.
<voice_0x01001BAB><se_low>It's Maurice.: Like I said before, my dream has come true. It's been a dream for a long time.
<voice_0x01001BAC><se_low>It's Maurice.: Now it is my turn to help Mori and Rajaso make their dreams come true.
<voice_0x01001BAD><se_low>It's Maurice.: Let the adventure commence with you! Do you like this pack?
<voice_0x01001BAE><se_low>It's Maurice.: Try on this dress, I know you said so!
<voice_0x01001BAF><se_low>It's Maurice.: Boy, I don't know what you're dreaming. But I know that Maui played an important role in making my dream come true.
Morris joins the team!
<voice_0x01001BB0><se_low>It's Maurice.: to the next!
<voice_0x01001BB1><se_low>King of tricks: The number of followers seems to be increasing. after retiring
<voice_0x01001BB2><se_low>King of tricks: I think it's better for you or other people from now on.
<voice_0x01001BB3><se_low>King of tricks: Yeah, I know what you're thinking, but someone's got to be. This way you won't reach narrow caves.
<voice_0x01001BB4><se_low>King of tricks: Of course, if someone brings something important to you, ask them to bring it.
<voice_0x01001BB5><se_low>It's Maurice.: It will surely be a good travel companion. Wait for me at sea!
<voice_0x01001BAE><se_low>It's Maurice.: Try on this dress, I know you said so!
<voice_0x01001BAF><se_low>It's Maurice.: Boy, I don't know what you're dreaming. But I know that Maui played an important role in making my dream come true.
<voice_0x01001BB6><se_high>Bridesmaid: Hmm... I thought you told Molly you didn't want us to be together.
<voice_0x01001BB7><se_low>It's Maurice.: A ninth! Consider the ghosts I held in my brother's chains.
<voice_0x01001BB8><se_low>It's Maurice.: No, do not say this! take me
<voice_0x01001BB9><se_low>It's Maurice.: I'll finish you asap and call for help. Enjoy
<voice_0x01001BBA><se_low>It's Maurice.: Well, that's it... Now that you've made your choice, I'm not going to force you to do it.
<voice_0x01001BBB><se_low>It's Maurice.: But who knows, maybe one day you too will need the joy that the forest alone can bring to your party. Will you be here when that day comes?
<voice_0x01001BBC><se_low>It's Maurice.: In the meantime, I'll be here waiting for you, honey.
<voice_0x01001BBD><se_low>It's Maurice.: oh ray! changed your mind
<voice_0x010013C3><se_high>Dye: Alright, see you on the boat.
<voice_0x01000A65><se_low>King of tricks: I'll wait for you in the car.
<voice_0x01000A66><se_low>King of tricks: I'm happy!
